rows.label: qst200818_0010
rows.name:
Onee-chan! Thanks for guardin'
the Grandarbor and everyone!

rows.label: qst200818_0020
rows.name:
I can't take all the credit.
Everyone else pitched in too!

rows.label: qst200818_0030
rows.name:
I wouldn't have been able
to save the tree without
my friends helping out.

rows.label: qst200818_0040
rows.name:
Some people may not care about
the environment, but there are
loads of people who do.

rows.label: qst200818_0050
rows.name:
I'm in the second camp! This
tree means a lot to me.

rows.label: qst200818_0060
rows.name:
Me too! It's the most
cherished thing we have here.

rows.label: qst200818_0070
rows.name:
That's wonderful. Please don't
change that way of thinking!

rows.label: qst200818_0090
rows.name:
I'd like you to stop calling
me 'Onee-chan.' You should
use 'Onii-chan', you know.
